Kabange Mupopo (amụrụ na 21 Septemba na afọ 1992) bụ onye Zambia na-agba ọsọ na onye na-agba bọọlụ, onye ritere ọla edo na 400m na afọ 2015 All-Africa Games

Mupopo malitere ịgba bọọlụ mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na otu, nke nwanne ya nwoke kpaliri. Ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Green Buffaloes FC na ndị otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Zambia; dị ka onyeisi ndị otu, ọ duuru Zambia gaa asọmpi asọmpi asọmpị ụmụ nwanyị nke Afrịka nke afọ 2014, ebe e wepụrụ ha n'ọkwa otu.

Mupopo malitere egwuregwu n'oge opupu ihe ubi nke afọ 2014, na-agba ọsọ 53.44 maka mita 400 na nzukọ mbụ ya. Ọ nọchitere anya Zambia na afọ 2014 Commonwealth Games na Glasgow, ebe ọ gbara ọsọ 53.09 ma wepụ ya na ọkara ikpeazụ. N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ, o nwetara ọlaọcha na 51.21 na African Championships na Marrakech, na-emebi ihe ndekọ Zambia; ọ tụfuru ọla edo na Folashade Abugan nke Naijiria, onye gbara ọsọ n'otu oge ahụ, na foto-ọgwụ. Mupopo ruru eru ịnọchite anya Africa na afo 2014 IAAF Continental Cup, kwa na Marrakech, ebe ọ nọ n'ọnọdụ nke anọ ma melite ndekọ mba ya ruo 50.87. Mupopo natara agụmakwụkwọ egwuregwu ọnwa iri na asatọ site na Kọmitii Olympic nke Zambia na afọ 2015, nke mere ka ọ lekwasị anya na egwuregwu ọ bụghị bọọlụ.

Mupopo malitere na IAAF Diamond League na Doha na ọnwa Mee, na afọ 2015, na-etinye nke asaa na 51.88. N'ọnwa Julaị afọ 2015 ọ gbara ọsọ 50.86 na La Chaux-de-Fonds, na-emeziwanye ihe ndekọ mba ya site na otu narị nke abụọ
A họpụtara ya maka asọmpi afọ 2015 World Championships na Beijing.
